Source.SQL Query:
select ZONES.ID as ID,
    ZONES.NAME as NAME,
    ZONES."LEVEL" as "LEVEL",
    ZONES.DEFEND_DAY_OF_WEEK as DEFEND_DAY_OF_WEEK,
    ZONES.DEFEND_UTC_TIME as DEFEND_UTC_TIME,
    ZONES.DEFEND_EASTERN_DAY as DEFEND_EASTERN_DAY,
    ZONES.DEFEND_EASTERN_TIME as DEFEND_EASTERN_TIME,
    ZONES.NOTES as NOTES,
    ZONES.OWNER_ID as OWNER_ID,
    ZONES.NEXT_DEFEND as NEXT_DEFEND,
    FROM_TZ( CAST( NEXT_DEFEND AS TIMESTAMP ), 'UTC' ) AT LOCAL AS NEXT_DEFEND_LOCAL,
    ZONES.MODIFIED_BY as MODIFIED_BY,
    ZONES.MODIFIED_DATE as MODIFIED_DATE 
 from ZONES ZONES
where OWNER_ID = :P5_ID

select z.ID,
       z.NAME || ' (' || "LEVEL" || '^) - ' || a.acronym TITLE,
       "LEVEL",
       OWNER_ID,
       CAST(from_tz(NEXT_DEFEND, 'UTC') at time zone 'America/New_York' AS TIMESTAMP) AS NEXT_DEFEND,
       CAST(from_tz(NEXT_DEFEND, 'UTC') at time zone 'America/New_York' AS TIMESTAMP) + (CASE "LEVEL"
            WHEN 1 THEN 1/24/2
            WHEN 2 THEN 1/24/4*3
            ELSE 1/24 END
        )
       AS END_DEFEND
  from ZONES z
INNER JOIN ALLIANCES a ON (a.ID = z.OWNER_ID)
 where OWNER_ID = :P5_ID
OR OWNER_ID IN (
    SELECT ID
    FROM ALLIANCES
    WHERE ALLIANCE_GROUP_ID IS NOT NULL
    AND  ALLIANCE_GROUP_ID IN (
        SELECT ALLIANCE_GROUP_ID
        FROM ALLIANCES
        WHERE ID = :P5_ID
        AND ALLIANCE_GROUP_ID IS NOT NULL
    )
)

Settings.PL\/SQL Code:
INSERT INTO ALLIANCE_SERVICES (ALLIANCE_ID, ZONE_SERVICE_ID, LEVEL_ID)
(
    SELECT z.OWNER_ID, zs.ID, 0 LEVEL_ID
    FROM ZONE_SERVICES zs
    INNER JOIN ZONES z ON (z.ID = zs.ZONE_ID)
    LEFT OUTER JOIN ALLIANCE_SERVICES aserv ON (
        aserv.ALLIANCE_ID = z.OWNER_ID
        AND aserv.ZONE_SERVICE_ID = zs.ID
    )
    WHERE z.OWNER_ID = :P5_ID
    AND aserv.ID IS NULL
);
